    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: August 28, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, SAN FRANCISCO",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: REPORTS OF FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "ATTENTION: ASSISTANT DIRECTOR D. M. LADD",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "On August 27, 1947, Lt. Colonel [REDACTED] A-2, Fourth Air",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Force, Hamilton Field, California, advised that the Area Intelligence Require-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "ments Division Office of the Assistant Chief of Staff, A-2 Headquarters, re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "quested that one [REDACTED] of Phoenix, Arizona, be completely inter-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "viewed in connection with a report that he had seen on July 7, 1947, what",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "he believed were flying discs. [REDACTED] is supposed to have taken several pic-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "tures of the discs with a 620 Box Camera.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "A previous report of this reported sighting of flying discs was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "forwarded the Bureau on August 8, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Colonel [REDACTED] has advised that [REDACTED], an",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "intelligence agent of A-2 stationed at Long Beach, California, would arrive",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "in Phoenix, Arizona, on or about September 2, 1947, and would be instructed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "to contact the Phoenix Field Division Office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "In accordance with Bureau Bulletin No. 42, Series 1947, it is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "felt that an agent from the Phoenix Field Division should interview [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Phoenix, if [REDACTED] has not already been",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "interviewed. Colonel [REDACTED] indicated that Mr. [REDACTED] should, if possible,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "sit in on this interview.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "A copy of the report from A-2 dated August 4, 1947, along with three",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "photographic prints of the pictures allegedly taken by Mr. [REDACTED], is being",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "enclosed for the Phoenix Field Division.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
